## Checklists

### Pull Request Checklist

- [ ] Domain code added under correct `src/domains/<domain>`
- [ ] No forbidden imports across boundaries
- [ ] Imports use path aliases where available (no deep relative paths)
- [ ] No re-export barrels (`index.ts` re-exports) introduced
- [ ] Routes added to `app/router.tsx` (if applicable)
- [ ] i18n keys added and referenced
- [ ] Tests added/updated (unit/E2E as needed)
- [ ] Accessibility reviewed (labels, focus, contrast)
- [ ] Performance reviewed (lazy loading, memoization where needed)
- [ ] Security reviewed (no secrets, safe HTTP usage)
- [ ] Docs updated (.mdc if structure/flows changed)
- [ ] `tsconfig` variants present and aligned: base, app, node, vitest, build

### Release Readiness

- [ ] Feature flags defaulted safely
- [ ] Analytics events tracked
- [ ] Error boundaries cover new pages
- [ ] Env variables documented in `core/config/env.ts`
- [ ] ESLint boundaries rules configured and passing
- [ ] `tsconfig.base.json` with aliases is present and referenced
- [ ] `tsconfig` variants exist as needed (node/vitest/build) and CI uses them appropriately
